            description="Volunteer in the TrainIT program as a Project Manager. TrainIT is a free educational program and job simulation community, which offers experience through participation in non-profit multidisciplinary MVPs, accompanied by seniors in different work niches. The goal is for participants to expand their portfolios and improve their professional profile vis-Ã -vis active companies in the market."
